Three Boplaas Ports were included in the SA Hall of Fame. The Boplaas Cape Vintage Reserve, Boplaas Cape Vintage and Boplaas Cape Tawny all made it into the Top 10 SA Hall of Fame.The Boplaas Ports have a fantastic record and won the SA Champion Port trophy (SAJWS) 9 times and won 15 Platter 5 stars, 22 Veritas Double gold medals and several Grand d Or at Michelangelo. Boplaas also won the Cappa Challenge for best SA Port on 6 occasions. Boplaas Ports are made from Touriga Nacional, Tinta Barocca and Souzao and made according to traditional methods in open lagars.